#. </p><p>
msgctxt "thig5.5:2.1"
msgid "Pañcakanipāta"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thig5.5:3.1"
msgid "5. Nanduttarātherīgāthā"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc87"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts87"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.5:4.1"
msgid "“Aggiṃ candañca sūriyañca,"
msgstr "In the past I honoured"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:4.2"
msgid "devatā ca namassihaṃ;"
msgstr "Fire, moon, sun, devas"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:4.3"
msgid "Nadītitthāni gantvāna,"
msgstr "Having gone to river-fording places "

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:4.4"
msgid "udakaṃ oruhāmihaṃ."
msgstr "I descended into the water"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc88"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts88"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.5:5.1"
msgid "Bahūvatasamādānā,"
msgstr "Observing many rules"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:5.2"
msgid "aḍḍhaṃ sīsassa olikhiṃ;"
msgstr "I shaved half my head"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:5.3"
msgid "Chamāya seyyaṃ kappemi,"
msgstr "Preparing a bed on the ground"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:5.4"
msgid "rattiṃ bhattaṃ na bhuñjahaṃ."
msgstr "I didn't eat food at night"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc89"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts89"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.5:6.1"
msgid "Vibhūsāmaṇḍanaratā,"
msgstr "Delighting in ornaments and decoration"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:6.2"
msgid "nhāpanucchādanehi ca;"
msgstr "Bathing and anointing"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:6.3"
msgid "Upakāsiṃ imaṃ kāyaṃ,"
msgstr "I looked after the body"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:6.4"
msgid "kāmarāgena aṭṭitā."
msgstr "Afflicted with desire for sensual pleasure"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc90"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts90"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.5:7.1"
msgid "Tato saddhaṃ labhitvāna,"
msgstr "Having gained faith"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:7.2"
msgid "pabbajiṃ anagāriyaṃ;"
msgstr "I went forth into homelessness"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:7.3"
msgid "Disvā kāyaṃ yathābhūtaṃ,"
msgstr "Seeing the body in its real essence"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:7.4"
msgid "kāmarāgo samūhato."
msgstr "Desire for sensual pleasure is uprooted"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc91"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts91"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.5:8.1"
msgid "Sabbe bhavā samucchinnā,"
msgstr "I've cut off all existence"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:8.2"
msgid "icchā ca patthanāpi ca;"
msgstr "Wishes and aspirations too"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:8.3"
msgid "Sabbayogavisaṃyuttā,"
msgstr "Disconnected from all bonds"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thig5.5:8.4"
msgid "santiṃ pāpuṇi cetaso”ti."
msgstr "I've realised peace of mind"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="6"></a>
msgctxt "thig5.5:9.1"
msgid "…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "thig5.5:9.2"
msgid "Nanduttarā therī …."
msgstr ""

